    <string name="gambaran_umum">Smart PTSL application is an application that helps accelerate the work of Complete Systematic Land Registration (PTSL). The SmartPTSL application is a GIS (Geography Information System) based application that is run on android media with features that have been tailored to PTSL needs. SmatPTSL application is not a measuring tool but a medium for pouring measurement numbers from meet band, aerial photo interpretation and connection to external GNSS.
    </string>
